      <title>WPF问题解决之自定义按钮样式</title>
      <link href="/2018/04/18/WPF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E4%B9%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F/"/>
      <url>/2018/04/18/WPF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E4%B9%8B%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>最近准备给公司写个新的小程序，厌倦了之前无脑的WinForm，这次开始折腾WPF。看了一些教程，由于有前端基础，觉得还挺好理解的，不过实际操作起来碰到了不少稀奇古怪的问题，总觉的前面还有一万个坑在等着我。</p><p>既然用了WPF，界面也必须设计的酷炫一些，这次想设计出一种破解注册机风格的，但毕竟不懂设计，也只好成这样意思意思。</p><img src="/2018/04/18/WPF问题解决之自定义按钮样式/3.png" title="界面"><p>做成上图的按钮样式非常简单，视频教程里也都有,敲入以下代码就解决了。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Window.Resources&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;Style x:Key=&quot;ButtonStyle&quot; TargetType=&quot;&#123;x:Type Button&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!--设定普通状态下样式--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;FontSize&quot; Value=&quot;12&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Background&quot; Value=&quot;#00DDDDDD&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BorderBrush&quot; Value=&quot;#FFDEDEDE&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Foreground&quot; Value=&quot;#FFE4E4E4&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/Style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/Window.Resources&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>但是执行预览时问题就来了，鼠标移动到按钮上，激活了系统按钮预设的样式，在我这个风格下非常难看。</p><img src="/2018/04/18/WPF问题解决之自定义按钮样式/4.png" title="ButtonError"><p>随后网上查了查，很多解决方案也只能部分解决我的问题，我自己拼凑了下，重复试了不少次，解决了这个问题，代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Window.Resources&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;Style x:Key=&quot;ButtonStyle&quot; TargetType=&quot;&#123;x:Type Button&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!--设定普通状态下样式--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;FontSize&quot; Value=&quot;12&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Background&quot; Value=&quot;#00DDDDDD&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BorderBrush&quot; Value=&quot;#FFDEDEDE&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Foreground&quot; Value=&quot;#FFE4E4E4&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!--自定义模板，覆盖掉触发MouseOver行为后的默认样式--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Template&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;Setter.Value&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;ControlTemplate TargetType=&quot;&#123;x:Type Button&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;Border x:Name=&quot;BorderBinder&quot; Background=&quot;#00DEDEDE&quot; BorderThickness=&quot;&#123;TemplateBinding BorderThickness&#125;&quot; </span><br><span class="line">                                BorderBrush=&quot;#FFE4E4E4&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                            &lt;ContentPresenter HorizontalAlignment=&quot;Center&quot; VerticalAlignment=&quot;Center&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;/Border&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;ControlTemplate.Triggers&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                            &lt;Trigger Property=&quot;IsMouseOver&quot; Value=&quot;True&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                &lt;!--TargetName属性的设置是一个要点，与Border中相关属性绑定，不然没有效果--&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Background&quot; TargetName=&quot;BorderBinder&quot; Value=&quot;#00000000&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;BorderBrush&quot; TargetName=&quot;BorderBinder&quot; Value=&quot;#FF00DCFF&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                                &lt;Setter Property=&quot;Foreground&quot; Value=&quot;#FF00DCFF&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                            &lt;/Trigger&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;/ControlTemplate.Triggers&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;/ControlTemplate&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;/Setter.Value&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/Setter&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/Style&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/Window.Resources&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用上边的样式，我的按钮在鼠标指针经过前后就有了以下的区别<br><img src="/2018/04/18/WPF问题解决之自定义按钮样式/1.png" title="This is problem image"><br><img src="/2018/04/18/WPF问题解决之自定义按钮样式/2.png" title="This is problem image"></p><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>因为WPF中对于按钮系统是套用模版，简单修改格式并不能改变特殊状态下的样式，比如<strong>IsMouseOver</strong>、<strong>IsFocused</strong>等。因此想要达到预期效果必须自定义模版。</p><p>上边代码中<strong>ControlTemplate</strong>下的<strong>Border</strong>相当于自己画了个按钮模版提交给系统，随后再使用触发器修改特定行为下的样式。</p><p><strong>需要注意的是</strong>，触发器内部修改的属性需要和之前Border中响应的属性进行Target绑定，不然完全没效果。</p>]]></content>
      
